Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.22,1:09:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can be, sometimes.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.22,1:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.22,1:10:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.22,1:10:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I find that sometimes they could benefit from some clearing...\NYeah.
