Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.48,1:11:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NMm-hmm .
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.48,1:11:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I really don't even have to know what the product is.\NThe body knows.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.48,1:11:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm .\NMm-hmm .
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.48,1:11:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, you know, a lot of people will choose to get on the remedy and they do get better.\NOf course, sometimes, you know, I need to refer them.
