Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.80,1:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking multiple questions here.\NYou want to become a teacher of TM?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.80,1:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\NNo?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.80,1:13:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was saying I've been placed in an unlikely position to hold some folks accountable within\Nthat movement, and I was curious to know your opinion about the TM movement.
