Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.34,1:13:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My son was murdered last year at the Maharishi University of Management.\NUh-huh .
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.34,1:13:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm involved in some moral decisions and some issues, and legal issues.\NAnd I'm curious to know your opinion of the TM movement, as well as Maharishi Mahesh Yogi,
