Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.70,1:13:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.70,1:13:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.70,1:13:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.70,1:13:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.57,1:13:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I got Mêmeh, though, at a wrong time, right here in Atlanta.\NThere's only about 290, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.22,1:14:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I personally felt that it was commercialized.\NI felt it got commercialized.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.11,1:14:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you why.\NBecause spiritual truth stands on its own, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.27,1:14:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can't really peddle it and bring in proselytite followers and use it to manipulate\Nthings.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.92,1:14:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So I felt that, although it had promise, it wasn't comprehended in an overall, pristine\Nway you know how it played into the consequences in your life I really can't
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.77,1:14:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,say you know so you believe it was essentially commercialized and perhaps\Nwell my my feeling is there a number of very helpful techniques out there but
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.36,1:15:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,then what happens is they get peddled see and then you and this followers you\Nget sort of multi-level marketing and the whole thing the intention now
