Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.13,1:15:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,probably serves a certain certain function it's like selling training and\Nhow to do the cities you know I'm saying
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.84,1:15:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's five thousand dollars uh-huh I understand your agony and indecision you\Nknow just by prayer you try to do what you think is the best thing you can do
